[start section id="20148"]

Discussed the risks, benefits, and alternatives of the procedure of exploratory laparotomy, right hemicolectomy and of possible blood transfusion.  Discussed advance directives and the necessity of other members of the healthcare team participating in the procedure.  All questions answered and consent given.

[end section id="20148"]

